data.title: Gitega Airport (GID) in Gitega, Burundi
data.meta_description: Create, visualize, track and map your flights from Gitega Airport using our flight mapper. It lies in Gitega, Burundi and has the IATA code of (GID)
data.text: Gitega Airport was an airport serving the city of Gitega, the current capital of Burundi. The airport was on a low ridge in the northwest section of the city.
